---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---
<ServiceLayout
    title="Custom AI Solutions – Super Sonic"
    description="Custom AI-powered systems designed to remove friction and unlock scale across your business."
    canonicalUrl="https://supersonic.media/ai-solutions/"
>
    <section class="service-hero">
        <div class="tag">Custom AI Solutions</div>
        <h1>Automation that creates <span class="gold">leverage.</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Custom AI-powered systems designed to remove friction and unlock scale.</p>
        <div class="hero-line"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="overview">
        <div class="overview-inner">
            <div class="overview-text">
                <div class="overview-label">Overview</div>
                <p>AI is only valuable when it&#8217;s operational.</p>
                <p>We design and implement intelligent workflows that connect your tools, eliminate repetitive work, and improve response time across your business.</p>
                <p><strong>No gimmicks. No &#8220;AI for the sake of AI.&#8221; Only systems that create measurable efficiency.</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="overview-principles">
                <div class="principle reveal"><h4>Where the bottleneck is</h4><p>We identify the manual processes costing you the most time and money.</p></div>
                <div class="principle reveal"><h4>What can be automated</h4><p>Not everything should be. We focus on high-impact, repeatable workflows.</p></div>
                <div class="principle reveal"><h4>How systems connect</h4><p>Your tools should talk to each other without human intervention.</p></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="deliver">
        <div class="section-tag">What We Deliver</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Intelligent systems that do the work for you.</h2>
        <div class="deliver-grid">
            <div class="deliver-card reveal">
                <div class="deliver-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Lead Intelligence</h3>
                <p>Automatically qualify, route, and prioritize incoming inquiries.</p>
                <div class="deliver-items"><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Lead scoring</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Intelligent routing</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Automated responses</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="deliver-card reveal">
                <div class="deliver-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="23 4 23 10 17 10"/><path d="M20.49 15a9 9 0 11-2.12-9.36L23 10"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Workflow Automation</h3>
                <p>Remove manual tasks that slow your team down.</p>
                <div class="deliver-items"><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Onboarding sequences</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Internal approval flows</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Notification systems</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Data syncing across platforms</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="deliver-card reveal">
                <div class="deliver-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="18" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"/><path d="M6 21V9a9 9 0 009 9"/></svg></div>
                <h3>System Architecture</h3>
                <p>We connect your tools into one coherent workflow.</p>
                <div class="deliver-items"><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>API integrations</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Automation logic mapping</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Custom workflow design</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Reporting layers</span></div></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="performance">
        <div class="perf-header">
            <div class="section-tag">The Goal</div>
            <h2>Built with intent.</h2>
            <p>AI should support your business &#8212; not complicate it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="perf-grid">
            <div class="perf-item reveal"><div class="perf-icon">&#9201;</div><h3>Reduce Manual Effort</h3><p>Automate the repetitive tasks that eat your team&#8217;s time.</p></div>
            <div class="perf-item reveal"><div class="perf-icon">&#128640;</div><h3>Increase Speed</h3><p>Respond faster, process faster, close faster.</p></div>
            <div class="perf-item reveal"><div class="perf-icon">&#128279;</div><h3>Connect Systems</h3><p>One workflow across all your tools &#8212; no more silos.</p></div>
            <div class="perf-item reveal"><div class="perf-icon">&#128208;</div><h3>Operational Clarity</h3><p>See what&#8217;s happening across your business in real time.</p></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ideal">
        <div class="ideal-inner">
            <div class="section-tag">Ideal For</div>
            <h2>Is this the right fit?</h2>
            <div class="ideal-items">
                <div class="ideal-item reveal"><span class="ideal-arrow">&#8594;</span><span>Growing teams feeling operational strain</span></div>
                <div class="ideal-item reveal"><span class="ideal-arrow">&#8594;</span><span>Businesses juggling disconnected tools</span></div>
                <div class="ideal-item reveal"><span class="ideal-arrow">&#8594;</span><span>Founders who want systems, not more staff</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="service-cta">
        <div class="cta-bg"></div>
        <h2>Let&#8217;s design the system behind <span class="gold">your growth.</span></h2>
        <p class="cta-sub">Tell us where the friction is. We&#8217;ll build the solution.</p>
        <div class="cta-btn-wrap">
            <a href="/start/" class="btn-primary">Start the Conversation <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 13L13 3M13 3H5M13 3v8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
        </div>
    </section>
</ServiceLayout>
